      <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.25rem; padding: 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #0c4a6e;">
        <li>Select an employee, month, and year</li>
        <li>Enter overtime dates and time entries (AM/PM sessions)</li>
        <li>System automatically calculates COC earned based on day type</li>
        <li>Weekday (5PM-7PM): 1.0x rate, max 2 hours</li>
        <li>Weekend/Holiday: 1.5x rate for 8AM-12PM and 1PM-5PM</li>
        <li>All entries saved as "Uncertified" until certificate is generated</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

